body:
25.06.2005 - 25.06.2019

hi. i‘m marie (she/her) and i‘m 22 y/o. my mom died 14 years ago. so naturally i‘m always wearing black on this day.. but it also needs to be a t-shirt * that i love, that comforts me. i chose my „have the courage to exist“ t-shirt because it‘s exactly what i need(ed). i just wanted to say thank you to @danielhowell for making this possible. you/he will never know how much this means to me.

* in june it’s usually very hot in germany
